{"tid":475212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【J到出血】支那核動力太空打飛機4小時到月球","createTime":"2017-11-21T02:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T06:03:02.000Z","uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2334edab38f20eb9bd4f75554ddb7bb4418320a4","tid":475212,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:19:44.000Z","msg":"【J到出血】支那未來航天飛機或將使用核動力4個小時可抵月球<br />\n<br />\n2017年11月20日10:59 新浪軍事<br />\n<br />\n近日，在支那航天科技集團相關媒體上刊登了支那未來新一代火箭計劃，其中的長八火箭和長九火箭登月大家都已有初步了解，而其中更遠景計劃中2040年的核動力空間穿梭機則引起了大家的興趣，究竟何為穿梭機，核動力空間穿梭機和普通穿梭機有何區別呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/mil/crawl/20171120/4a5k-fynwnty5657568.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fmil%2Fcrawl%2F20171120%2F4a5k-fynwnty5657568.jpg&h=59ec07ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n　　首先，所謂穿梭機，即shuttle，意為天地往返的運輸工具，其穿梭機，有玉女穿梭之意， 即象織布的梭子一樣重複往返，而其典型範例就是航天飛機，美國於上世紀70年代開始研製航天飛機，在80年代前後實現首飛，其主燃料箱利用了阿波羅登月計劃中土星五號火箭的成果，而之後的俄羅斯也研製了能源暴風雪航天飛機，雖然因為蘇聯解體而終止，但其副產品，RD171&amp;RD170&amp;RD180火箭發動機至今仍為人們所津津樂道，其最大推力甚至創造了單發火箭發動機的世界紀錄，超過了800噸，至今仍沒有其他國家所突破，而其高空補燃液氧煤油發動機技術，仍然是很多國家望塵莫及，無法突破的禁地。而之後美版的空天飛機先導機也是穿梭機的典型代表，其比一代航天飛機，更有利於在空氣和近地軌道飛行，在空氣和近地軌道機動能力更強，也可以和航天飛機一樣，以飛機形式降落，同時在軌能力也更長。<br />\n <br />\n　　但以上所說穿梭機主要在航天和航空領域，並沒涉及星際間探索，及太陽系中的旅行，而且其採用的動力也是化學能源動力，而在支那2040年遠景規劃中的核動力空間穿梭機，卻採用核動力，可能的工作方式為最新的電磁驅動引擎，即通過核動力的熱離子堆產生電能，然後通過電磁驅動引擎來推進穿梭機前進，據悉，電磁驅動引擎的速度已經超過目前已知的所有航天器的速度，包括之前號稱最快的太陽帆動力，電磁驅動將意味著衛星等太空載具將不再需要藉助助推化學燃料，其能量將來自於反射微波所帶來的巨大能量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/mil/crawl/20171120/5qw6-fynwnty5657594.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fmil%2Fcrawl%2F20171120%2F5qw6-fynwnty5657594.jpg&h=0e39fd6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另有報導稱，作為一種革命性的太空引擎，這種新引擎將在未來的星際旅行中派上大用場，也就是只需10週時間即可到達火星。到達月球的時間則只需4個小時。<br />\n　　<br />\n究竟情況如何還有待核實確認，但可以說支那航天的未來很精彩，我們也有支那自己的星際旅行之夢，畢竟我們的目標是星辰大海。（作者署名：浩漢防務）<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n  　本欄目所有文章目的在於傳遞更多信息，並不代表本網贊同其觀點和對其真實性負責。凡本網註明版權所有的作品，版權均屬於新浪網，凡署名作者的，版權則屬原作者或出版人所有，未經本網或作者授權不得轉載、摘編或利用其它方式使用上述作品。<br />\n<br />\n　　新浪軍事：最多支那軍事迷首選的打飛機門戶！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mil.news.sina.com.cn/jssd/2017-11-20/doc-ifynwnty5659836.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmil.news.sina.com.cn%2Fjssd%2F2017-11-20%2Fdoc-ifynwnty5659836.shtml&d=YHB6s8ga2I4eb32L6MIQwPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5357d257\" target=\"_blank\">http://mil.news.sina.com.cn/jssd/2017-11-20/doc-ifynwnty5659836.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"8c74167a7a41bcfd7ca8bbd9149ccd23b02fc465","tid":475212,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:21:36.000Z","msg":"支那人嫦娥要幾耐？"},{"pid":"c3bfa8749149ffa487d73387dec134aa560f3102","tid":475212,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:22:42.000Z","msg":"NASA玩到 Orion 啦, 穿梭機已經被美帝退役左好耐, 概念已OUT<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/thumbnails/image/23128844405_6151e276cd_k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fthumbnails%2Fimage%2F23128844405_6151e276cd_k.jpg&h=125acb5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d33a30570236f0352d2abcbcd61620b2e28baf1","tid":475212,"uid":73262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:23:40.000Z","msg":"其實佢發展緊核武"},{"pid":"7188a8581a79964da82b8379c4bf6884f113161b","tid":475212,"uid":2189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:29:15.000Z","msg":"核動力都同太陽帆比？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f6bb15ad751196866936d72af317f329543880","tid":475212,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遠景計劃中2040年的核動力空間穿梭機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2040年支那國仲係咪存在緊?"},{"pid":"877152a744af56e812bde8127c260ce850e89f26","tid":475212,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>核動力都同太陽帆比？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSpace shuttle design 唔理啦, Nuclear electric 都唔知有咩好打飛機, 想喺度 FF RF Resonant Cavity 都唔關 solar/electric/magnetic sail 以至 chemical propulsion 事啦擺明唔識亂比"},{"pid":"8f2d8261e4e77d06bf40a37ea2470ec87d3c44dd","tid":475212,"uid":80198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:27:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>遠景計劃中2040年的核動力空間穿梭機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2040年支那國仲係咪存在緊?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算共產黨倒台，都會有另一個政權取代架嘛"},{"pid":"49bb7fe401b05506ea35c6037bd09df8606719b3","tid":475212,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:31:19.000Z","msg":"月球都是中國的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af97fed9591bfedbe3f100d401fe02b05cd4568","tid":475212,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>遠景計劃中2040年的核動力空間穿梭機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2040年支那國仲係咪存在緊?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算共產黨倒台，都會有另一個政權取代架嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔比分裂既?"},{"pid":"9199b22d041a2e6c7bb49f77a3d38a90f6557a06","tid":475212,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>據悉，電磁驅動引擎的速度已經超過目前已知的所有航天器的速度，包括之前號稱最快的太陽帆動力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛機咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  太空阻力極低，基本上你加速到幾多就有幾快<br />\n話你隻野飛得快過人地真係呃外行人<br />\n<br />\n另外，你唔跟最省油既軌道飛去咪可以行快d，但晒多好多油<br />\n你有本事咪直線飛去火星然後再減速"},{"pid":"ce3d61705f4db652bf8a4bc32e1c863d9003513a","tid":475212,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"原來上月球 = 上天國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b71cb664678fbab0958763624e677404555019","tid":475212,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:45:32.000Z","msg":"仲上月球？今時今日梗係登陸太陽啦"},{"pid":"bdef7dd4149229894f8127f3d9d0692879e7b0bb","tid":475212,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T05:43:00.000Z","msg":"冚球剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37ff71e06eac1cb08a3a2670c652bf520e8efe6","tid":475212,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T05:44:25.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解美國唔用核動力火箭<br />\n一小小差錯就會全球核污染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那你唔好咁癡線啦"},{"pid":"72e57fac575b5d427481011a3774f05e6e6934d7","tid":475212,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>知唔知點解美國唔用核動力火箭<br />\n一小小差錯就會全球核污染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那你唔好咁癡線啦</blockquote><br />\n又唔會全球核污染<br />\n<br />\n人地美國50年前玩完成功埋<br />\n只係個project終止左冇玩落去"}]}